data.eml:eml: Two new marine species of Cocconeis (Bacillariophyceae) from the west coast of Sweden

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Al-Handal, Adil Y., Riaux-Gobin, Catherine, Jahn, Regine, Wulff, Angela Katarina, Minerovic, Alison (2019): Two new marine species of Cocconeis (Bacillariophyceae) from the west coast of Sweden. European Journal of Taxonomy 497: 1-16, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5852/ejt.2019.497
